  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Samurthi officer was killed while waiting for fuel in Pothuvil",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police in Ampara Pothuvil said that a Samurthi officer fainted and died while waiting in line for fuel in Amparai Pothuvil.",
        "51-year-old Dissanayaka, who was working as a Samurthi officer from Lagukalai in Pothu, died in this way.",
        "He was waiting to get petrol from the Co-operative filling station in Pothu since the morning of the incident, when he fell unconscious and died due to a heart attack.",
        "Police said that he had undergone cardiac surgery and the body was taken to Pottu Hospital for post-mortem examination."
      ],
